text: nowpel del keat bankheunh preah chnt reah laeng keat ban pol tha nih kuchea mcheasa robsakhnhom . te nowpel preah chnt lich bat towvinh keat kaban pol tha pitabrakd nasa brasenbae kmean kar changaoulobangheanh pi mcheasa robsakhnhom te khnhom pitchea sthetnow knongchamnaom puok del v nge v ng cheaminkhan
